<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="absent-adj">absent <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˈæbsənt/    美 /ˈæbsənt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>缺席的；不在的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>be <strong>absent from</strong> class / work
缺课/缺勤</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>缺乏的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Snow is absent in some countries. 
有些国家终年无雪。</p></div></div>